時，應保持鎮定及盡量與牠們保持距離，切勿主動走近或引起牠們的注意，更不應用物件拋向或驅趕牠們，以免發生危險。<br />\n如市民受野豬滋擾，或發現野豬誤闖或被困市區，可致電 1823 通知漁農自然護理署（漁護署）。漁護署會派員到場了解野豬出現的原因，並就防止野豬滋擾提供意見。如有需要時，漁護署會派員到場驅趕或捕捉野豬。 一旦人身安全受到威脅，應立即致電 999 通知警方派員到場採取行動，以保護安全。"},{"pid":"4b90dfd835539073ae3b3f7addf8823b9f46d2cf","tid":2064500,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:52:50.000Z","msg":"推，不能只有我看到"},{"pid":"6b98c785de59e427cde1fd46c725ff46487298d0","tid":2064500,"uid":53672,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"條女都幾顛 日日po咸相 同av女優無分別"},{"pid":"e4fdfd0e7d95c3b5736f1cded999bf041d62fea7","tid":2064500,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf0e583bbd3684ef5581dfa79d4fbb6ba8662ffb","tid":2064500,"uid":206382,"like":22,"dislike":96,"score":-74,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gY493Sy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgY493Sy.png&h=70201267&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f54d540c29b882b4f9b28d0296621eeac32397a","tid":2064500,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"叫佢燒自己啲相比梁烈士j算啦"},{"pid":"f571094e78dff0797346c03f1bae7ad31483b242","tid":2064500,"uid":11849,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:54:18.000Z","msg":"買佢相果啲垃撚圾"},{"pid":"6fed2a19b0b39d683ef6853642acf46baf57fd8f","tid":2064500,"uid":34571,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"6b98c785de59e427cde1fd46c725ff46487298d0","tid":2064500,"uid":53672,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"條女都幾顛 日日po咸相 同av女優無分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T00:54:33.000Z","msg":"佢一見留言有人讚佢唔肥就出晒水"},{"pid":"7a5778837b408cddca405ddd49b60caa6e22a255"